茂禄驴<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><Bill RHead_reign="62 Eliz. II" RHead_ParlYear="2013" DocumentTitle="BILL C-557" Bill_No="C-557" Document_No="411766" xml:lang="EN" Bill_Type="Non-amending" Stage_Name="First-Reading-House" Reprint="No" xml:space="preserve" ChapterNo_E="C. " ChapterNo_F="ch. " Bill-Origin="commons"><Bill_Part Part_Type="Cover" CountLines="No"><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="CovBillNo">C-557</Para></Block><Block><Para TopMargin="24" Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" TextAlign="Center">Second Session, Forty-first Parliament,</Para></Block><Block><Para Size="9" Leading="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" TextAlign="Center">62 Elizabeth II, 2013</Para></Block><Block><Para TopMargin="48" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Bold="Yes" TextAlign="Center">HOUSE OF COMMONS OF CANADA</Para></Block><Block><Para TopMargin="42" Size="18" Leading="20" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Bold="Yes" TextAlign="Center">BILL C-557</Para></Block><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="CovLongTitle">An Act to amend the Navigable Waters Protection Act (Vancouver Island)</Para></Block><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="COV_StageLine"></Para></Block><Block><Para Size="9" AllCaps="Yes" Hyphenate="OFF">first reading, December 2, 2013</Para></Block><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="COV_StageLine"></Para></Block><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="Cover_Sponsors"><SC SC_PerCent="85">Mr. Garrison</SC></Para></Block><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="Cover_DocNo">411766</Para></Block></Bill_Part><Bill_Part CountLines="No" Part_Type="InsideCover"><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="BPT_InsideCoverE">Available on the Parliament of Canada Web Site at the following address:<br /><B>http://www.parl.gc.ca</B></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><Para TopMargin="108" BottomMargin="4" Size="10" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center">SUMMARY</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" Size="8" Leading="9" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify">This enactment amends the <I>Navigable Waters Protection Act</I> in order to add five lakes and one river on Vancouver Island to the navigable waters listed in the schedule to that Act, as it will read immediately after the coming into force of section 331 of the <I>Jobs and Growth Act, 2012</I>.</Para></Block></Bill_Part><Bill_Part Part_Type="MainText" CountLines="Yes" RunningHead_E="Navigable Waters Protection (Vancouver Island)"><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="MainText_DocNo">411766</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="Session_Reign">2nd Session, 41st Parliament,</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="Session_Reign">62 Elizabeth II, 2013</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="MainBillOrigin">house of commons of canada</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Bold="Yes" Style="MAIN@BillNo_Title">BILL C-557</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes"><Para Style="MAIN@ti;04">An Act to amend the Navigable Waters Protection Act (Vancouver Island)</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify">Her Majesty, by and with the advice and consent of the Senate and House of Commons of Canada, enacts as follows:</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><!--Heading:NAVIGABLE WATERS PROTECTION ACT--><MarginalNote>R.S., c. N-22<br /></MarginalNote><Para TopMargin="10" Bold="Yes" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center">NAVIGABLE WATERS PROTECTION ACT</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Bold="Yes"><B>1.</B> Part 1 of the schedule to the <I>Navigable Waters Protection Act</I>, as it reads immediately after the coming into force of section 331 of the <I>Jobs and Growth Act, 2012</I>, is amended by adding after item 2 in the columns shown the following:</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹2.1芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Nimpkish Lake芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹50脗掳24芒聙虏01芒聙鲁 N, 126脗掳58芒聙虏33芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹The lake芒聙聶s water boundary includes the mouths of all connecting waterways芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹2.2芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Kennedy Lake芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹49脗掳03芒聙虏35芒聙鲁 N, 125脗掳33芒聙虏15芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹The lake芒聙聶s water boundary includes the mouths of all connecting waterways芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹2.3芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Great Central Lake芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹49脗掳21芒聙虏00芒聙鲁 N, 125脗掳15芒聙虏00芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹The lake芒聙聶s water boundary includes the mouths of all connecting waterways芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹2.4芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Sproat Lake芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹49脗掳16芒聙虏09芒聙鲁 N, 125脗掳03芒聙虏35芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹The lake芒聙聶s water boundary includes the mouths of all connecting waterways芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹2.5芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Horne Lake芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹49脗掳20芒聙虏32芒聙鲁 N, 124脗掳42芒聙虏01芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹The lake芒聙聶s water boundary includes the mouths of all connecting waterways芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Bold="Yes"><B>2.</B> Part 2 of the schedule to the Act is amended by adding after item 3 in the columns shown the following:</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Item: 芒聙聹3.1芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 1: 芒聙聹Campbell River芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 2: 芒聙聹50脗掳02芒聙虏55芒聙鲁 N, 125脗掳15芒聙虏30芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 3: 芒聙聹49脗掳50芒聙虏18芒聙鲁 N, 125脗掳37芒聙虏16芒聙鲁 W芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="No"><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="0" Hyphenate="ON" TextAlign="Justify"><change>Column 4: 芒聙聹From Buttle Lake to the Strait of Georgia芒聙聺</change></Para></Block><Block LineCnt="N" Align="Yes" KeepWith="Next"><!--Heading:COMING INTO FORCE--><Para TopMargin="10" Bold="Yes" Hyphenate="OFF" TextAlign="Center">COMING INTO FORCE</Para></Block><Block LineCnt="Y" Align="Yes"><MarginalNote>Coming into force<br /></MarginalNote><Para TopMargin="5" LeftMargin="0" FirstLineIndent="2" Bold="Yes"><B>3.</B> This Act comes into force on the later of the day section 331 of the <I>Jobs and Growth Act</I>, 2012 comes into force and the day on which this Act receives royal assent.</Para></Block><Block Align="Yes"><Para Style="BPT_ImprintE"><br /><br />Published under authority of the Speaker of the House of Commons</Para></Block><Block Align="Yes" LineCnt="N"><Para NoLineBreak="Yes" NoHtml="Yes" Leading="0" Size="0" TopMargin="0" BottomMargin="0">脗聞</Para></Block></Bill_Part></Bill>